WEBVTT

00:00.801 --> 00:03.637
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

01:00.994 --> 01:02.430
COPS ARE OFTEN ASKED

01:02.430 --> 01:04.965
IF THEY BELIEVE
THEY'RE DOING GOD'S WORK.

01:04.965 --> 01:06.567
OFFICER BEN SHERMAN

01:06.567 --> 01:09.837
IS JUST TRYING TO DO THE JOB
WITHOUT LOSING HIS SOUL.

01:13.207 --> 01:16.110
SOMETHING WAS...
JUST WRONG

01:16.110 --> 01:18.946
ABOUT THE WAY SHE WAS
HOVERING OVER THAT KID.

01:18.946 --> 01:20.748
DO YOU THINK
SHE'S A GOOD COP?

01:23.083 --> 01:24.685
SHE'S SQUARED AWAY.

01:24.685 --> 01:28.656
SO YOU GOT TO TRUST HER
TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

01:28.656 --> 01:32.960
YOU DON'T REGRET NOT BLOWING
THE WHISTLE AT RAMPART?

01:32.960 --> 01:35.629
WHY YOU THINK
I STARTED USING?

01:37.498 --> 01:39.733
WE HAD A LOT OF GOOD COPS
AT RAMPART.

01:39.733 --> 01:43.571
A COUPLE OF THEM STARTED CUTTING
CORNERS TO GET THE JOB DONE.

01:43.571 --> 01:45.239
FELLOW OFFICERS, FRIENDS.

01:45.239 --> 01:47.808
I GAVE THEM
THE BENEFIT OF THE DOUBT.

01:48.776 --> 01:51.312
YOU SURE THAT WAS
THE RIGHT DECISION?

01:51.312 --> 01:53.247
HELL, NO.

01:53.247 --> 01:55.783
BUT YOU ONLY GOT
TWO CHOICES.

01:55.783 --> 01:58.852
AND GUESS WHAT --
THEY BOTH SUCK.

01:58.852 --> 02:01.389
[ DUCKS QUACKING ]

02:03.557 --> 02:06.360
HEY. DID YOU CATCH
A CASE LAST NIGHT?

02:06.360 --> 02:08.429
MM. I COULDN'T SLEEP.

02:08.429 --> 02:11.799
GAS AND PEEING
EVERY FIVE MINUTES.

02:11.799 --> 02:14.134
AM I EVER GONNA
GET MY iPAD BACK?

02:14.134 --> 02:17.238
NO, I LIKE READING
ON THIS THING.

02:17.238 --> 02:19.273
STEVE JOBS WAS ADOPTED.

02:19.273 --> 02:22.576
HE FORGAVE HIS MOTHER
FOR GIVING HIM AWAY,

02:22.576 --> 02:27.080
AND HIS BIOLOGICAL SISTER
BECAME ONE OF HIS BEST FRIENDS.

02:27.080 --> 02:29.450
AND?

02:29.450 --> 02:32.820
HE NEVER FORGAVE HIS FATHER --
NEVER GOT TO KNOW HIM.

02:32.820 --> 02:36.824
CHILDREN NEED TO KNOW
WHERE THEY COME FROM.

02:36.824 --> 02:38.959
THAT BABY'S GONNA WANT TO
KNOW HIS FATHER.

02:38.959 --> 02:41.529
I NEVER SHOULD HAVE DOWNLOADED
THAT BOOK FOR YOU.

02:41.529 --> 02:45.533
Rucker: L.A.P.D. GIVES YOU
A GUN, PARTNERS,

02:45.533 --> 02:48.836
AND AIR SUPPORT --
EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO SURVIVE.

02:48.836 --> 02:52.840
BUT WE DON'T TEACH YOU
HOW TO COPE WHEN YOU GET HOME.

02:52.840 --> 02:55.643
ALL COPS BURN OUT...

02:55.643 --> 02:56.910
GET TO THE POINT

02:56.910 --> 02:59.947
WHERE THERE'S NO ONE
YOU FEEL YOU CAN TALK TO --

02:59.947 --> 03:04.952
NOT YOUR PASTOR
AND DEFINITELY NOT YOUR SPOUSE.

03:04.952 --> 03:08.322
THIS BOOK WILL HELP YOU STAY
IN TOUCH WITH WHAT'S IMPORTANT.

03:08.322 --> 03:10.558
DISMISSED.

03:10.558 --> 03:13.661
STEARN, HASPEL,
TAKE THE DAMN BOOK.

03:13.661 --> 03:14.595
[ SIGHS ]

03:14.595 --> 03:17.197
WHAT'S NEXT,
MANDATORY COP BOOK CLUB?

03:17.197 --> 03:18.766
ARE WE ALL
GONNA GET TOGETHER,

03:18.766 --> 03:20.934
DRINK HERBAL TEA,
AND READ PROUST?

03:23.771 --> 03:24.938
[ SIGHS ]

03:29.076 --> 03:31.279
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
GOT MY SERGEANTS ORAL.

03:31.279 --> 03:34.748
I'M GONNA TRY TO CATCH A FEW
MINUTES HERE AND THERE TO STUDY.

03:34.748 --> 03:36.684
IT'S YOUR LUCKY DAY.

03:37.885 --> 03:41.422
Ben: "WHEN YOU HEAR THE
PHRASE 'SCOUT LEADER,'
WHAT COMES TO MIND?"

03:42.856 --> 03:47.094
"IF YOU ANSWERED 'PEDOPHILE,'
YOU'RE A BURNT-OUT COP."

03:47.094 --> 03:48.362
BOOK'S OUTDATED.

03:48.362 --> 03:50.998
"COACH"
IS A BETTER PHRASE.

03:50.998 --> 03:52.900
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

03:54.435 --> 03:56.270
"AFTER YOU GET HOME
FROM WORK,

03:56.270 --> 04:00.107
DO YOU HAVE A MAGIC CHAIR WHERE
YOU LIKE TO SIT TO DECOMPRESS?"

04:00.107 --> 04:04.878
I HAD A MAGIC HOTEL BED ONCE,
BUT IT TOOK QUARTERS.

04:04.878 --> 04:05.846
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:05.846 --> 04:07.147
[ CHUCKLES ] SEE?

04:07.147 --> 04:09.650
SEE, I KNEW YOU COULDN'T KEEP
THIS STOIC CRAP UP FOREVER.

04:09.650 --> 04:10.584
STUPID.

04:10.584 --> 04:13.220
WELCOME BACK, BRYANT.
WELCOME BACK.

04:13.220 --> 04:14.755
HEY --
HEY, CHECK IT OUT.

04:17.391 --> 04:20.260
[ BRAKES SQUEAK,
CAR DOORS OPEN ]

04:20.260 --> 04:21.529
SIR?

04:21.529 --> 04:24.197
YOU ALL RIGHT?

04:24.197 --> 04:25.499
YEAH.

04:25.499 --> 04:27.868
I JUST GOT MUGGED.

04:27.868 --> 04:28.802
YEAH?

04:28.802 --> 04:29.770
YEAH.

04:32.005 --> 04:33.741
WHAT'D THEY TAKE?

04:33.741 --> 04:34.608
MY PHONE.

04:34.608 --> 04:36.344
WHAT'S YOUR NAME, SIR?

04:36.344 --> 04:40.013
FATHER GREG CARMICHAEL.
PEOPLE CALL ME FATHER C.

04:45.185 --> 04:46.219
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

04:46.219 --> 04:47.488
Ruben:
HERE'S MY CARD.

04:47.488 --> 04:48.856
GIVE ME A CALL
IF YOU HEAR ANYTHING ELSE

04:48.856 --> 04:50.691
OR YOU HAVE ANYTHING ELSE
YOU WANT TO TELL ME.

04:50.691 --> 04:52.025
YOU'VE BEEN REALLY HELPFUL.

04:52.025 --> 04:54.094
IT'S A LONG WAY DOWN.

04:54.094 --> 04:55.429
PSH.

04:55.429 --> 04:57.498
SHE MUST HAVE DROPPED THIS
BEFORE SHE JUMPED.

04:57.498 --> 05:00.033
IS THERE ANYTHING ON IT?

05:00.033 --> 05:03.036
UNSENT TEXT MESSAGE.

05:03.036 --> 05:05.406
"YOU CAN'T KEEP IGNORING ME."

05:05.406 --> 05:07.375
WHO WAS SHE SENDING IT TO?

05:07.375 --> 05:09.910
SHE HADN'T ENTERED IN
A NUMBER YET.

05:09.910 --> 05:11.278
THINK IT'S A SUICIDE?

05:11.278 --> 05:13.681
MM, THEY DIDN'T FIND
A NOTE NEAR THE BODY

05:13.681 --> 05:16.517
AND DOESN'T LOOK LIKE
THERE'S ONE IN THE PURSE.

05:16.517 --> 05:19.052
MAYBE SHE LEFT IT
AT HOME?

05:19.052 --> 05:21.722
KICKED OFF A SHOE
BEFORE SHE JUMPED?

05:21.722 --> 05:23.924
YEAH.
YEAH, IT'S A ROBBERY.

05:23.924 --> 05:25.693
ROBBERY GONE WRONG, HUH?

05:25.693 --> 05:28.996
NO. WALLET'S IN THE PURSE
WITH CASH IN IT.

05:28.996 --> 05:32.433
YOU KNOW THE OFFICER BELOW
CALLED HER A SPLAT?

05:32.433 --> 05:34.468
[ SCOFFS ]
GALLOWS HUMOR.

05:34.468 --> 05:36.604
WHATEVER GETS YOU THROUGH IT,
I GUESS.

05:36.604 --> 05:38.539
YEAH, WELL, I PRAY.

05:38.539 --> 05:40.974
I'M A LITTLE PRAYED OUT.

05:40.974 --> 05:45.846
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

05:45.846 --> 05:47.347
GIVE ME THE PHONE.
NO, I GOT IT.

05:47.347 --> 05:48.882
NO, NO. THEY'RE EXPECTING
TO HEAR A WOMAN'S VOICE.

05:48.882 --> 05:50.484
YOU DON'T WANT TO
SPOOK THEM.

05:50.484 --> 05:53.821
OH, RIGHT. AND HEARING YOU
WON'T DO THAT. HERE.

05:56.289 --> 05:57.891
HELLO?

05:57.891 --> 06:01.562
I'M DETECTIVE LYDIA ADAMS,
LOS ANGELES POLICE DEPARTMENT.

06:01.562 --> 06:03.864
WHO AM I SPEAKING WITH?

06:03.864 --> 06:07.367
MA'AM,
I NEED YOU TO CALM DOWN.

06:07.367 --> 06:08.769
JUST BREATHE.

06:08.769 --> 06:12.473
DO YOU OWN
A MERCEDES S.U.V.?

06:13.641 --> 06:16.343
MA'AM, PLEASE
JUST BREATHE, OKAY?

06:16.343 --> 06:19.179
I'M GONNA SEND A PATROL UNIT
TO YOU.

06:19.179 --> 06:21.582
OKAY.
I'VE GOT IT.

06:21.582 --> 06:23.617
MA'AM, CALM DOWN.

06:23.617 --> 06:26.186
WE'LL TALK AS SOON
AS YOU GET HERE, OKAY?

06:26.186 --> 06:27.721
ALL RIGHT.

06:30.458 --> 06:32.225
[ SIGHS ]
OUR VICTIM WAS A NANNY.

06:32.225 --> 06:34.361
SHE HAD TWO KIDS WITH HER.

06:34.361 --> 06:35.629
LET THEM KNOW.

06:35.629 --> 06:37.631
YO!
GUYS.

06:41.702 --> 06:43.871
CANDACE IS 6,
AND TYLER'S 4.

06:43.871 --> 06:47.007
AND YOU'RE SURE THEY WERE
WITH MISS JUAREZ.

06:47.007 --> 06:49.877
YES. I SPOKE WITH HER
A FEW HOURS AGO.

06:49.877 --> 06:51.712
HAVE YOU NOTICED ANYTHING
UNUSUAL ABOUT HER LATELY --

06:51.712 --> 06:54.848
MOOD SWINGS, DEPRESSION,
ANYTHING OUT OF THE ORDINARY?

06:54.848 --> 06:56.116
NEVER.

06:56.116 --> 06:58.952
THE MORE STRESSED OUT AT WORK
I WAS, THE CALMER SHE WAS.

06:58.952 --> 07:01.421
I HAD TO TRAVEL SO MUCH FOR WORK
AND MY HUSBAND, TOO,

07:01.421 --> 07:04.558
AND SHE WOULD STAY AT THE HOUSE
WITH THEM WHEN WE WERE GONE.

07:04.558 --> 07:06.193
SHE WAS WONDERFUL
WITH THEM.

07:06.193 --> 07:07.528
SO, WHAT ABOUT YOUR HUSBAND

07:07.528 --> 07:09.296
OR ANY OTHER FAMILY MEMBERS
OR FRIENDS?

07:09.296 --> 07:11.965
DID SHE MAYBE DROP THEM OFF,
DO SOME SHOPPING?

07:11.965 --> 07:14.768
NO, SHE KNEW ONLY TO LEAVE
THE KIDS WITH ME OR WITH ERIC.

07:14.768 --> 07:15.903
AND ERIC'S YOUR HUSBAND.

07:15.903 --> 07:17.671
HAVE YOU BEEN ABLE
TO REACH HIM?

07:17.671 --> 07:19.640
NOT YET.
HE'S NOT ANSWERING HIS CELL.

07:19.640 --> 07:21.875
BUT WHEN HE'S ON DEADLINE,
HE GETS LIKE THAT.

07:21.875 --> 07:23.977
OKAY, WE'RE GONNA DO
EVERYTHING WE CAN

07:23.977 --> 07:26.046
TO GET YOUR CHILDREN BACK,
OKAY?

07:26.046 --> 07:27.047
THANK YOU.

07:29.917 --> 07:32.720
[ SIGHS ] THESE KIDS
COULD BE ANYWHERE BY NOW.

07:32.720 --> 07:35.556
SURE YOU DON'T NEED
A DOCTOR?

07:35.556 --> 07:37.057
NO, I'M FINE.

07:37.057 --> 07:39.259
IF YOU GUYS COULD JUST
TAKE ME BACK TO THE RECTORY,

07:39.259 --> 07:40.694
THAT'D BE GREAT.

07:40.694 --> 07:42.530
MAYBE WE SHOULD DRIVE AROUND
A BIT,

07:42.530 --> 07:44.665
SEE IF WE CAN FIND THE PUNKS
THAT JUMPED YOU.

07:44.665 --> 07:47.400
NO,
I'M NOT GONNA PRESS CHARGES.

07:47.400 --> 07:50.370
MAYBE WE COULD
FIND YOUR PHONE.

07:50.370 --> 07:52.239
I CAN BUY ANOTHER PHONE.

07:52.239 --> 07:53.807
NOT THE POINT, FATHER.

07:53.807 --> 07:55.676
Ben: ARE YOU NEW?

07:55.676 --> 07:57.878
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU AROUND
BLESSED SACRAMENT BEFORE.

07:57.878 --> 08:00.080
YEAH, I JUST GOT TRANSFERRED
DOWN HERE FROM MODESTO.

08:00.080 --> 08:02.683
DIFFERENT KIND OF FLOCK
DOWN HERE, PADRE, EH?

08:02.683 --> 08:04.384
ASK YOU A QUESTION,
FATHER?

08:04.384 --> 08:05.519
YEAH, SURE.

08:05.519 --> 08:07.988
WHY DON'T YOU
WEAR A COLLAR?

08:07.988 --> 08:09.723
YOU KNOW,
SOMETIMES THAT COLLAR

08:09.723 --> 08:11.725
KEEPS PEOPLE AWAY
FROM THE CHURCH.

08:11.725 --> 08:14.695
SOMETIMES THE CHURCH KEEPS
PEOPLE AWAY FROM THE CHURCH.

08:14.695 --> 08:18.131
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU RELIGIOUS, OFFICER?

08:18.131 --> 08:20.233
JEW...ISH.

08:20.233 --> 08:22.803
OBSERVANT?

08:22.803 --> 08:26.139
TRY TO KEEP MY EYES OPEN
OUT HERE FATHER. YEAH.

08:26.139 --> 08:27.507
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:27.507 --> 08:30.678
YOU SHOULD WEAR YOUR COLLAR
IN THIS NEIGHBORHOOD, FATHER.

08:30.678 --> 08:33.046
THAT WILL KEEP YOU
FROM GETTING MUGGED.

08:33.046 --> 08:35.048
THINK SO, HUH?

08:35.048 --> 08:38.451
GOT TO WEAR A UNIFORM
DOWN HERE.

08:38.451 --> 08:42.990
BLOOD, CRIP, VATO,
PRIEST, COP.

08:42.990 --> 08:44.992
IF PEOPLE DON'T KNOW
WHAT GANG YOU'RE FROM,

08:44.992 --> 08:47.661
YOU'RE JUST A VICTIM
DOWN HERE.

08:48.729 --> 08:50.698
GOT TO SHOW YOUR COLORS.

08:50.698 --> 08:52.065
THAT'S RIGHT.

08:52.065 --> 08:54.401
HE WAS THE NBA's SIXTH MAN
OF THE YEAR LAST SEASON.

08:54.401 --> 08:57.337
YOU DON'T JUST LET A GUY
LIKE THAT GET AWAY, YOU KNOW?

08:57.337 --> 08:59.372
NAIL IN THE COFFIN
IS WHEN HE WENT KARDASHIAN

08:59.372 --> 09:02.142
AND THEN JUST GOT ALL PISSED
WHEN THEY TRIED TO DEAL HIM.

09:02.142 --> 09:03.176
BITCH MOVE.

09:03.176 --> 09:04.845
ANYTHING ABOUT THAT KID
YOU SHOT?

09:04.845 --> 09:07.014
YEAH, STILL NOT AWAKE.

09:08.415 --> 09:12.085
I DON'T BLAME LAMAR FOR,
YOU KNOW, DEMANDING A TRADE.

09:12.085 --> 09:13.120
COULDN'T TRUST THEM.

09:13.120 --> 09:14.888
THEY SHOULD HAVE
JUST IGNORED HIM,

09:14.888 --> 09:16.624
KEPT THINGS
THE WAY THEY WERE

09:16.624 --> 09:18.291
ONCE THEY LOST OUT
ON CHRIS PAUL.

09:18.291 --> 09:21.862
DISPATCHER: A57, shots fired,
Capitol Records building.

09:21.862 --> 09:24.564
[ SIGHS ]
A57. SHOW US RESPONDING.

09:24.564 --> 09:27.000
[ SIREN WAILS ]

09:27.000 --> 09:30.503
Tank: SEE, BACK IN THE DAY,
OH, WASN'T ABOUT NO GUN PLAY.

09:30.503 --> 09:32.673
NO.
YOU HAD TO FIGHT.

09:32.673 --> 09:34.441
YEAH. THUNDERDOME.

09:34.441 --> 09:36.644
LOOK, SOMETIMES YOU WIN.

09:36.644 --> 09:39.647
SOMETIMES YOU LOSE.

09:41.248 --> 09:42.716
BUT YOU LIVE, HOMEY.

09:42.716 --> 09:45.719
YOU LIVE TO FIGHT ANOTHER DAY.
[ CLAPPING ]

09:47.888 --> 09:49.389
Sammy:
THAT IS TOUCHING.

09:49.389 --> 09:52.192
DR. KING -- HE WOULD HAVE
TEARS IN HIS EYES FROM THAT.

09:52.192 --> 09:54.427
WHAT'S GOING ON, MAN?
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?
I GOT A QUESTION FOR YOU.

09:54.427 --> 09:59.166
WHEN DID THE FIVE TRES START
BEATING UP ON PRIESTS, HUH?

09:59.166 --> 10:00.400
WHAT?

10:00.400 --> 10:01.802
Sammy:
OH, YEAH, YEAH.

10:01.802 --> 10:05.472
ONE OF YOUR GUYS BEAT UP
FATHER CARMICHAEL OVER THERE

10:05.472 --> 10:06.974
AND TOOK HIS PHONE.

10:06.974 --> 10:08.508
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

10:08.508 --> 10:09.777
HOLD UP, HOLD UP, HOLD UP.

10:09.777 --> 10:11.679
NOT NONE OF MINE.
YOU'RE A GODDAMN LIAR.

10:11.679 --> 10:12.913
NO?

10:12.913 --> 10:16.149
I KNOW ONE OF Y'ALL
HAS A WARRANT.

10:16.149 --> 10:18.085
I JUST KNOW IT.

10:18.085 --> 10:20.954
I TOSS YOUR POCKETS,
ONE OF YOU ALL IS HOLDING.

10:20.954 --> 10:22.422
ASK THE QUESTION, SHERMAN.

10:22.422 --> 10:24.958
WHO WANTS TO GO TO JAIL?
WHO WANTS TO GO HOME?

10:24.958 --> 10:27.928
HMM? I GET A PHONE,
AND WE LEAVE.

10:27.928 --> 10:29.362
NO HARM, NO FOUL.

10:29.362 --> 10:32.199
ONE-TIME HAIL MARY
BECAUSE OF FATHER C.

10:32.199 --> 10:34.702
HE'S MORE FORGIVING
THAN I AM.

10:34.702 --> 10:37.738
BRYANT, AIN'T NOBODY
STOLE NO PHONE, MAN.

10:37.738 --> 10:40.240
RECOGNIZE ANYBODY, FATHER?

10:40.240 --> 10:42.609
I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE.
I DON'T KNOW.

10:42.609 --> 10:43.677
NO?

10:43.677 --> 10:45.679
FOUND THIS
ON THE GROUND.

10:45.679 --> 10:49.049
[ SCOFFS ]
JESUS CHRIST.

10:49.049 --> 10:50.317
HEY.

10:50.317 --> 10:52.452
Sammy: A MIRACLE.

10:52.452 --> 10:53.887
DIVINE INTERVENTION

10:53.887 --> 10:55.655
COURTESY OF THE LOS ANGELES
POLICE DEPARTMENT.

10:55.655 --> 10:57.725
COME HERE, HOMEY.
WHAT'S UP WITH YOU, MAN?

10:57.725 --> 10:59.459
OH, SHIT.

10:59.459 --> 11:02.329
I MEAN, HALLELUJAH.

11:02.329 --> 11:04.898
[ SIREN WAILING ]

11:08.836 --> 11:12.205
DROP THE GUN!
DROP THE GUN!

11:12.205 --> 11:14.274
Man: SHE SHOT ME!
HE WAS COMING AFTER ME!

11:14.274 --> 11:16.476
BACK UP.
FACE FORWARD.
SHE SHOT ME!

11:16.476 --> 11:17.644
BACK UP.

11:17.644 --> 11:19.112
YOU GOT ANYTHING ON YOU?
I GOT NOTHING!

11:19.112 --> 11:20.781
PUT YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR BACK.
[ MOANING ]

11:20.781 --> 11:24.217
A57. NEED AN R.A. UNIT, OUR
LOCATION, VICTIM OF A GUNSHOT,

11:24.217 --> 11:26.186
PARKING LOT BEHIND
CAPITOL RECORDS --

11:26.186 --> 11:29.957
CORNER ARGYLE AND YUCCA,
SOUTHEAST CORNER.

11:29.957 --> 11:31.558
HANG ON, BUDDY.
HE ATTACKED ME.

11:31.558 --> 11:34.161
[ COUGHS, GRUNTS ]

11:34.161 --> 11:35.562
OKAY.

11:35.562 --> 11:38.431
KEEP YOUR HEAD DOWN.
KEEP YOUR HEAD DOWN.
[ MOANING ]

11:38.431 --> 11:41.634
PERMISSION TO SAY
THIS IS A WASTE OF TIME?

11:41.634 --> 11:43.703
Lydia:
WHO ARE YOU TELLING?

11:43.703 --> 11:45.138
WOULDN'T EVEN BE HERE

11:45.138 --> 11:47.340
IF THE MOTHER WASN'T TOO BUSY
TO BE A MOTHER.

11:47.340 --> 11:49.943
OH, SO SHE'S SUPPOSED TO BE
MOPPING FLOORS

11:49.943 --> 11:52.712
AND BAKING CAKES
FOR HER HARD-WORKING HUSBAND?

11:52.712 --> 11:53.947
LOOK, THIS IS NOT
A SEXIST THING.

11:53.947 --> 11:55.315
THAT'S NOT
WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

11:55.315 --> 11:56.884
I'M JUST SAYING
WHAT'S BEST FOR THE KIDS.

11:56.884 --> 11:59.252
OKAY, SO IF A WOMAN
WANTS A CAREER AND A BABY,

11:59.252 --> 12:01.054
THAT MAKES HER
IRRESPONSIBLE.

12:01.054 --> 12:02.655
YOU'VE NEVER USED A NANNY?

12:02.655 --> 12:05.025
A WHAT?
COPS DON'T HAVE NANNIES.

12:05.025 --> 12:07.928
WE HAVE BABYSITTERS
AND MOTHER-IN-LAWS.

12:07.928 --> 12:10.063
AND IF YOU DON'T HAVE
A MOTHER-IN-LAW?

12:10.063 --> 12:12.933
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN IF IT'S
THE FATHER OR THE MOTHER,

12:12.933 --> 12:15.202
BUT SOMEBODY HAS TO
STAY THEIR ASS AT HOME.

12:15.202 --> 12:19.106
BOTTOM LINE, DON'T HAVE A KID
IF NOBODY HAS TIME TO RAISE IT.

12:19.106 --> 12:20.908
THAT'S ALL I'M SAYING.

12:30.250 --> 12:32.319
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
HEY. HEY.
IT'S OKAY.

12:32.319 --> 12:33.921
HEY. HEY, KIDS.
IT'S OKAY.

12:33.921 --> 12:36.156
Lydia:
ARE YOU CANDACE?

12:36.156 --> 12:37.290
YES.

12:37.290 --> 12:41.428
IS THIS YOUR BROTHER, TYLER?
THOSE ARE YOU GUYS?

12:41.428 --> 12:42.662
ARE YOU HURT?

12:42.662 --> 12:44.031
NO.

12:44.031 --> 12:45.765
YOU THINK YOU CAN TELL US
WHAT HAPPENED?

12:45.765 --> 12:52.105
I WAS ASLEEP, AND I WOKE UP
WHEN I HEARD YELLING.

12:52.105 --> 12:54.007
WAS VERONICA
YELLING AT SOMEONE,

12:54.007 --> 12:56.076
OR WAS SOMEBODY
YELLING AT VERONICA?

12:56.076 --> 12:58.946
THE MAN WAS YELLING AT HER
OUTSIDE.

12:58.946 --> 13:00.513
DID YOU SEE WHO HE WAS?

13:00.513 --> 13:04.484
DID YOU RECOGNIZE THE VOICE
OF THE MAN WHO WAS YELLING?

13:06.854 --> 13:08.288
I DON'T KNOW.

13:08.288 --> 13:09.622
THAT'S OKAY.

13:09.622 --> 13:12.092
YOU THINK YOU CAN TELL US
WHAT HAPPENED AFTER THAT?

13:12.092 --> 13:18.131
VERONICA SCREAMED...
AND THEN IT GOT REAL QUIET.

13:18.131 --> 13:21.534
VERONICA DIDN'T COME BACK.

13:21.534 --> 13:23.170
THIS IS IT RIGHT HERE.

13:23.170 --> 13:24.337
YEAH.

13:27.707 --> 13:30.277
YOU THINK THE GOOD FATHER
HAS ANY IDEA

13:30.277 --> 13:33.013
WHAT HE'S GETTING HIMSELF INTO
MOVING DOWN HERE FROM MODESTO?

13:33.013 --> 13:35.048
PROBABLY RENTED
THE "GRIDIRON GANG,"

13:35.048 --> 13:36.583
FIGURED HE GOT IT COVERED.

13:36.583 --> 13:38.151
YOU THE ONE THAT CALLED US?

13:38.151 --> 13:41.521
YES, SIR. I GOT PEOPLE IN MY
HOUSE, AND I WANT THEM OUT.

13:41.521 --> 13:42.722
SO ASK THEM TO LEAVE.

13:42.722 --> 13:44.091
I DON'T LIVE IN IT.

13:44.091 --> 13:45.592
I'M RENOVATING RIGHT NOW
AND TRYING TO SELL IT.

13:45.592 --> 13:47.427
EVERY FEW DAYS, PEOPLE BREAK
THE LOCK AND SNEAK IN,

13:47.427 --> 13:50.864
SLEEP ON THE FLOOR,
START FIRES IN THE FIREPLACE,

13:50.864 --> 13:52.265
MESS UP THE BATHROOMS.

13:52.265 --> 13:54.467
SO THERE'S PEOPLE IN THERE
NOW?

13:54.467 --> 13:56.836
THE LOCK'S BROKEN AGAIN.
I DIDN'T GO IN.

13:56.836 --> 13:59.372
LAST TIME, SOMEBODY TOOK A SWING
AT ME WITH A BROKEN BOTTLE.

13:59.372 --> 14:00.340
ALL RIGHT.

14:00.340 --> 14:02.509
WE'LL CHECK IT OUT.
STAY HERE.

14:02.509 --> 14:05.112
POLICE! WE'RE COMING IN!

14:19.126 --> 14:21.661
[ CLATTERING ]

14:21.661 --> 14:24.497
HEAR THAT?

15:08.675 --> 15:10.110
OKAY, WAKE UP.

15:12.312 --> 15:15.815
CRYSTAL?

15:15.815 --> 15:18.018
WAKE UP, CRYSTAL.

15:18.018 --> 15:22.055
GET YOUR ASS UP.
ALL OF YOU.

15:30.130 --> 15:33.500
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

15:33.500 --> 15:35.402
SHE'S JUST A KID!
Ben: YOU'RE OKAY.

15:35.402 --> 15:37.137
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

15:37.137 --> 15:39.539
YOU'RE OKAY. YOU'RE OKAY.
YOU'RE OKAY.

15:39.539 --> 15:41.108
COME HERE, BABY.

15:41.108 --> 15:45.078
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

15:48.681 --> 15:51.318
[ GRUNTS ]

15:53.220 --> 15:55.622
Tang: HEY, COOPER!
YOU SEE A WEAPON?

15:55.622 --> 15:56.923
NO.

15:56.923 --> 15:58.791
ARE YOU SURE THERE WAS A WEAPON?
DID YOU FIND ANYTHING?

15:58.791 --> 16:02.429
DID YOU -- DID YOU SEE HIM
THROW ANYTHING ANYWHERE?

16:02.429 --> 16:03.963
WHAT?

16:03.963 --> 16:05.465
A KNIFE OR A GUN?

16:05.465 --> 16:08.001
HE -- HE WAS YELLING,
AND HE WAS RUNNING UP BEHIND ME.

16:08.001 --> 16:10.870
I SAW HIM CHASING ME
WHEN I WAS CROSSING THE STREET.

16:10.870 --> 16:12.372
BUT HE WAS IN THE STORE,
TOO.

16:12.372 --> 16:14.107
HE WAS BEHIND ME
IN THE CHECKOUT LINE.

16:14.107 --> 16:15.442
HE WAS WATCHING ME.

16:15.442 --> 16:17.110
THIS YOURS?

16:17.110 --> 16:21.081
THOSE ARE MY K-KEYS.

16:21.081 --> 16:23.383
WHERE DID YOU FIND MY KEYS?

16:25.718 --> 16:29.522
OH...OH, GOD.

16:29.522 --> 16:32.425
WHAT WAS HE YELLING
WHEN HE RAN UP BEHIND YOU?

16:32.425 --> 16:35.262
I MUST HAVE -- I MUST HAVE
TOOK THEM OUT OF MY PURSE

16:35.262 --> 16:37.097
TO GET MY CHECKBOOK.

16:37.097 --> 16:39.632
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HE WAS YELLING?

16:39.632 --> 16:42.135
MA'AM?

16:42.135 --> 16:45.372
"YO. YO."

16:45.372 --> 16:47.840
HE WAS YELLING, "YO."

16:47.840 --> 16:48.775
YEAH.

16:53.146 --> 16:55.882
[ CRYING, SNIFFLES ]

16:55.882 --> 16:58.418
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

17:00.253 --> 17:03.190
Sammy: NO, I WAS NOT LATE.
LISTEN...

17:03.190 --> 17:05.092
Ben:
THAT DIDN'T TAKE LONG.

17:05.092 --> 17:07.127
MISDEMEANOR TRESPASSING.

17:07.127 --> 17:09.996
NOBODY'S DOING TIME
IN PELICAN BAY.

17:09.996 --> 17:13.633
IT'S CHEAPER TO POST BAIL
THAN IT IS TO PAY FOR AN
APARTMENT FOR THE GIRLS.

17:13.633 --> 17:14.967
GOT TO LOVE A PIMP.

17:14.967 --> 17:17.937
ALWAYS WATCHING OUT
FOR THE BOTTOM LINE.

17:17.937 --> 17:19.472
WHERE'S MY KID?

17:19.472 --> 17:22.942
YOU GONNA TAKE DANIELA
BACK OUT ON THE STREET WITH YOU?

17:22.942 --> 17:24.744
NO. WHERE IS SHE?

17:24.744 --> 17:28.148
WE'RE HOLDING HER UNTIL
FAMILY SERVICES CAN GET HERE

17:28.148 --> 17:29.616
TO DO AN EVALUATION.

17:29.616 --> 17:31.418
HOW LONG
IS THAT GONNA TAKE?

17:31.418 --> 17:34.387
COUNTY SERVICES, YOU KNOW,
SO I WOULDN'T HOLD MY BREATH.

17:34.387 --> 17:36.323
SHE NEEDS TO BE
WITH HER MAMA.

17:36.323 --> 17:38.024
OUT ON THE STREETS?
I DOUBT IT.

17:38.024 --> 17:39.626
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT MY BABY NEEDS.

17:39.626 --> 17:41.528
I'M THE ONLY FAMILY
SHE'S GOT.

17:43.096 --> 17:44.897
I GOT TO GO.

17:44.897 --> 17:46.799
YOU DON'T GOT TO GO.

17:46.799 --> 17:50.036
WE CAN HELP TAKE YOU AND DANIELA
OFF THE STREET.

17:50.036 --> 17:51.871
HE DOESN'T OWN YOU.

17:51.871 --> 17:53.273
HE PROTECTS ME.

17:53.273 --> 17:56.509
YEAH? SO WHY DO YOU
LOOK SO SCARED?

17:56.509 --> 17:58.345
TELL DANIELA
I'LL BE BACK FOR HER.

17:58.345 --> 18:00.079
[ RAP MUSIC PLAYS ]

18:00.079 --> 18:03.716
Sammy:
NICE TO KNOW AMERICAN NUCLEAR
FAMILIES AREN'T IN DECLINE.

18:03.716 --> 18:07.254
[ MUSIC CONTINUES ]

18:08.388 --> 18:11.658
SISTER'S COMING DOWN
TO SEE US AND I.D. THE BODY.

18:11.658 --> 18:15.362
AWFUL LOT OF CALLS FROM OUR
VICTIM'S PHONE TO THE HUSBAND'S.

18:15.362 --> 18:16.629
HE STILL AWOL?

18:16.629 --> 18:18.265
WIFEY SAID
SHE'D LET US KNOW

18:18.265 --> 18:19.666
WHEN SHE GOT IN CONTACT
WITH HIM.

18:19.666 --> 18:21.834
GUESS HE'S TOO BUSY
FOR WIFEY AND THE KIDS.

18:21.834 --> 18:24.271
YEAH, BUT NOT TOO BUSY
FOR THE NANNY, THOUGH,

18:24.271 --> 18:26.273
'CAUSE THERE WERE A LOT
OF TEXTS, TOO.

18:26.273 --> 18:29.642
BUT THEY WERE ALL
PASSWORD-PROTECTED BY SOME APP.

18:29.642 --> 18:32.245
THE LAB'S GONNA HAVE TO
CRACK IT.

18:32.245 --> 18:34.914
WELL, IT COULD BE
PICTURES OF THE KIDS.

18:34.914 --> 18:37.884
HEY, I KNOW MY BABYSITTER.
SHE DOES THAT ALL THE TIME.

18:37.884 --> 18:38.985
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

18:38.985 --> 18:40.620
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

18:40.620 --> 18:42.889
ADAMS.

18:42.889 --> 18:45.024
YEAH.

18:45.024 --> 18:47.960
OKAY. THANKS.

18:47.960 --> 18:52.499
LAB RESULTS CAME BACK NEGATIVE
FOR DRUGS, POSITIVE FOR BABY.

18:52.499 --> 18:54.801
YOU ASK THE SISTER
ABOUT A BOYFRIEND?

18:54.801 --> 18:56.035
YEAH.
[ CHUCKLES ]

18:56.035 --> 18:58.205
YEAH, SHE SAID
THAT VERONICA WORKED TOO MUCH

18:58.205 --> 18:59.806
TO HAVE A BOYFRIEND.

18:59.806 --> 19:02.642
SAID SHE SPENT MORE NIGHTS
AT WORK WHEN THE WIFE WAS AWAY

19:02.642 --> 19:04.544
THAN SHE DID
AT HER OWN PLACE.

19:04.544 --> 19:07.314
LITTLE CANDACE
COULDN'T IDENTIFY THE MALE VOICE

19:07.314 --> 19:09.115
THAT WAS ARGUING
WITH THE NANNY.

19:09.115 --> 19:11.218
THINK THAT DADDY
WAS GETTING BUSY WITH THE NANNY

19:11.218 --> 19:12.885
WHILE MOMMY WAS AWAY
ON BUSINESS?

19:12.885 --> 19:15.388
LITTLE KID WAS SCARED.
MAYBE SHE JUST DIDN'T
RECOGNIZE THE VOICE.

19:15.388 --> 19:18.925
MAYBE SHE'S TOO SCARED
TO SAY IT WAS HER DAD.
AND HE'S STILL MISSING.

19:18.925 --> 19:20.993
WE NEED TO FIND HIM.

19:20.993 --> 19:24.063
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

19:24.063 --> 19:26.132
I WAS RAPED TWO YEARS AGO.

19:26.132 --> 19:27.367
[ SNIFFLES ]

19:27.367 --> 19:30.870
GOING BACK TO MY CAR
AFTER A PARTY.

19:30.870 --> 19:35.575
AFTER THAT, I TOLD MYSELF...
NEVER AGAIN.

19:35.575 --> 19:38.345
GUY WHO RAPED YOU
WAS BLACK?

19:40.112 --> 19:41.914
[ Voice breaking ]
OH, GOD.

19:41.914 --> 19:45.084
HE WAS JUST TRYING TO
GIVE ME MY KEYS.

19:45.084 --> 19:46.953
[ CRYING ]

19:46.953 --> 19:48.588
[ SIGHS ]

19:48.588 --> 19:51.558
[ SNIFFLES ]
I'M GOING TO JAIL.

19:51.558 --> 19:54.294
YOU'RE GONNA BE TALKING TO
DETECTIVES BACK AT THE STATION.

19:54.294 --> 19:55.695
IT'S REALLY IMPORTANT

19:55.695 --> 19:57.464
THAT YOU TELL THEM THE TRUTH
ABOUT EVERYTHING, OKAY?

19:57.464 --> 19:59.832
TELL THEM THAT YOU WERE RAPED,
HOW YOU FELT SCARED,

19:59.832 --> 20:00.700
HOW YOU FELT THREATENED.

20:00.700 --> 20:02.435
DON'T LEAVE ANYTHING OUT,
OKAY?

20:10.377 --> 20:12.945
SHE MANAGED TO GET
SOME VERY INTERESTING ANGLES

20:12.945 --> 20:14.514
WITH HER iPHONE.

20:14.514 --> 20:16.816
YEAH. OOH. MM-HMM.

20:16.816 --> 20:19.118
HAVE MY WIFE
TRY THIS ONE TONIGHT.

20:19.118 --> 20:21.588
YOU NEED TO STOP BY
THE BATHROOM?

20:21.588 --> 20:24.524
YOU THINK THE WIFE KNEW
THAT THE NANNY

20:24.524 --> 20:26.993
WAS SENDING HER LOVING HUSBAND
SUCH EXQUISITE PHOTOS?

20:26.993 --> 20:28.395
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

20:28.395 --> 20:30.363
THINK HUBBY WAS GETTING
HIS FULL SCHWARZENEGGER ON.

20:30.363 --> 20:31.731
WE SHOW HER THESE PHOTOS,

20:31.731 --> 20:33.766
I BET SHE FIGURES OUT A WAY
TO FIND HIM FAST.

20:33.766 --> 20:36.536
YOU'RE FINALLY GETTING THE HANG
OF THIS LEVERAGE THING.

20:36.536 --> 20:38.638
I'M LEARNING FROM THE BEST,
PARTNER.

20:38.638 --> 20:40.373
MM.

20:52.285 --> 20:53.953
MY DAUGHTER'S GOT TO EAT.

20:53.953 --> 20:57.557
THEY'LL BE FEEDING HER IN
FOSTER CARE YOU KEEP THIS UP.

20:57.557 --> 21:00.693
YOU ARRESTING ME AGAIN?

21:02.795 --> 21:04.431
EVERY TIME
YOU TURN A TRICK,

21:04.431 --> 21:06.699
YOU GOT ENOUGH MONEY
FOR TWO BUS TICKETS.

21:06.699 --> 21:09.536
YOU AND DANIELA COULD BE
HALFWAY ACROSS THE COUNTRY

21:09.536 --> 21:11.704
BEFORE ANYBODY KNOWS
YOU'RE GONE.

21:11.704 --> 21:12.839
YEAH.

21:12.839 --> 21:14.907
AND GO WHERE?

21:14.907 --> 21:16.976
YOU WANT HER IN THE LIFE?

21:16.976 --> 21:19.278
THAT'S WHERE SHE'S HEADED.

21:19.278 --> 21:20.847
IT'S HER FATHER.

21:20.847 --> 21:23.350
[ RAP MUSIC PLAYING ]
WHO?

21:23.350 --> 21:25.752
RONNIE.

21:31.090 --> 21:32.592
WHAT'S UP?

21:32.592 --> 21:34.060
Ronnie:
WHAT'S UP WITH YOU?
GOT A PROBLEM?

21:34.060 --> 21:35.462
WHAT YOU WANT TO BE UP?
WHAT YOU WANT TO BE UP?

21:35.462 --> 21:36.563
GOT A PROBLEM?

21:36.563 --> 21:37.797
MAN,
YOU AIN'T SCARING NOBODY.

21:37.797 --> 21:39.332
WHAT'S UP YOUR ASS,
MOTHERFUCKER?

21:39.332 --> 21:40.400
WHAT YOU WANT TO BE UP?

21:40.400 --> 21:42.301
STAY RIGHT HERE.

21:44.604 --> 21:47.106
JUST LEAVE US ALONE,
ALL RIGHT?

21:47.106 --> 21:50.410
WE'RE DOING FINE.
OKAY?

21:55.348 --> 21:57.083
COME ON. BIG GUY.

21:57.083 --> 21:58.451
Cooper: BIG BLACK GUY.

21:58.451 --> 21:59.686
BIG ANY GUY.

21:59.686 --> 22:01.454
99% OF THE WOMEN
WHO'VE BEEN RAPED,

22:01.454 --> 22:03.523
SOME GUY RUN UP TO THEM,
SCREAMING "YO,"

22:03.523 --> 22:05.658
IF THEY'VE GOT A GUN,
THEY'RE GONNA SHOOT.

22:05.658 --> 22:07.527
IN BROAD DAYLIGHT
IN THE MIDDLE OF HOLLYWOOD

22:07.527 --> 22:09.596
WITH ALL THOSE PEOPLE
AROUND.

22:09.596 --> 22:11.898
SHE HAD A MILLION OPTIONS.

22:11.898 --> 22:17.069
INSTEAD, SHE PULLED THE GUN,
PLUGGED THE GUY IN THE GUT.

22:17.069 --> 22:18.438
[ SIGHS ]

22:18.438 --> 22:22.108
WELL, I GUESS SHE FELT BETTER
SAFE THAN SORRY.

22:23.976 --> 22:26.479
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

22:26.479 --> 22:28.948
YEAH, IT'S TANG.

22:28.948 --> 22:30.850
YEAH.

22:30.850 --> 22:32.885
THANKS FOR LETTING ME KNOW.

22:32.885 --> 22:34.654
THAT WAS HILL.
KID I SHOT WOKE UP.

22:34.654 --> 22:36.055
LOOKS LIKE
HE'S GONNA MAKE IT.

22:36.055 --> 22:38.558
HILL WANTS ME BACK
AT THE STATION RIGHT AWAY.

22:38.558 --> 22:40.126
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

22:40.126 --> 22:42.995
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

22:42.995 --> 22:44.997
WHAT IN THE HELL
DID WE CALL DCFS IN FOR

22:44.997 --> 22:46.999
IF YOU'RE JUST GONNA RELEASE HER
BACK TO HER HOOKER MOM?

22:46.999 --> 22:49.702
DON'T YELL AT ME.
I JUST GOT HERE.

22:49.702 --> 22:51.003
FINE. WHO WAS IT?

22:51.003 --> 22:53.239
DEEDEE COLE
DID THE EVALUATION.

22:53.239 --> 22:54.641
AND SHE JUST LET HER GO?

22:54.641 --> 22:55.875
DANIELA'S 13 YEARS OLD.

22:55.875 --> 22:57.877
HER MOTHER HAD HER LIVING
IN A SQUAT.

22:57.877 --> 23:01.213
SAYS HERE SHE WAS SIGNED OUT
TO HER FATHER, RONALD WATKINS.

23:01.213 --> 23:04.350
NO WARRANTS, NO PRIORS,
HAS A PERMANENT ADDRESS.

23:04.350 --> 23:07.086
[ SIGHS ]
SHE WAS RELEASED
INTO HIS CUSTODY.

23:07.086 --> 23:08.488
HE'S A PIMP.

23:08.488 --> 23:09.889
SO ARREST HIM.

23:09.889 --> 23:12.492
THEN WE CAN TRY TO
REMOVE HER FROM THE HOME.

23:12.492 --> 23:13.793
THAT'S IT?

23:13.793 --> 23:16.195
YOU'RE JUST GONNA
THROW HER ON THE STREET?

23:16.195 --> 23:19.098
SHE WAS RELEASED
TO A PARENT.

23:19.098 --> 23:21.868
SHE WAS IN A VACANT HOUSE
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE DAY.

23:21.868 --> 23:24.871
IF WE PULLED EVERY KID WE FOUND
TRESPASSING FROM THEIR PARENTS,

23:24.871 --> 23:27.440
HALF THE KIDS IN THE CITY
WOULD BE IN FOSTER CARE.

23:27.440 --> 23:28.841
TRY DOING YOUR JOB

23:28.841 --> 23:30.977
BEFORE YOU START COMPLAINING
ABOUT HOW I DO MINE.

23:30.977 --> 23:32.745
I'M TRYING TO
DO MY FUCKING JOB, LADY.
COME ON. COME ON.
COME ON.

23:32.745 --> 23:34.714
I'M TRYING TO
DO MY FUCKING JOB.
ALL RIGHT, LISTEN.

23:34.714 --> 23:37.083
YOU DID YOUR BEST,
MOTHER TERESA.

23:38.451 --> 23:41.854
I HONESTLY DON'T KNOW
WHERE HE IS.

23:41.854 --> 23:44.323
WHEN HE'S ON DEADLINE, HE CAN
DISAPPEAR FOR DAYS TO WRITE.

23:44.323 --> 23:45.592
WHY PROTECT HIM?

23:45.592 --> 23:46.993
I'M NOT. I SWEAR.

23:46.993 --> 23:49.596
I WOULD TELL YOU
IF I KNEW.

23:49.596 --> 23:52.732
I WANT TO KICK HIS ASS.

23:52.732 --> 23:55.267
I'M GLAD SHE JUMPED.

23:55.267 --> 23:58.671
IF I'D HAVE FOUND THESE, I MIGHT
HAVE PUSHED THE BITCH MYSELF.

23:58.671 --> 24:01.708
DID I SAY THAT OUT LOUD?

24:01.708 --> 24:03.510
YEAH, YOU DID.

24:03.510 --> 24:06.145
DISPATCHER: All units in the
vicinity of 51st and San Pedro,

24:06.145 --> 24:07.814
ADW in progress.

24:07.814 --> 24:10.717
A36.
SHOW US RESPONDING.

24:10.717 --> 24:13.285
36, Roger.
Handle code three.

24:13.285 --> 24:16.055
[ SIREN WAILING ]

24:16.055 --> 24:18.190
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

24:24.463 --> 24:25.965
DAMN IT.

24:30.236 --> 24:32.004
AMBER.

24:32.004 --> 24:34.707
A36, 51st STREET AND SAN PEDRO.

24:34.707 --> 24:36.943
NEED AN R.A. UNIT NOW.

24:36.943 --> 24:39.078
DISPATCHER:
Roger that, A36.

24:39.078 --> 24:41.113
AMBER.

24:41.113 --> 24:42.314
HER DAD.

24:42.314 --> 24:43.716
OKAY.

24:43.716 --> 24:45.552
KEEP THAT MOUTH OPEN.
KEEP THAT MOUTH OPEN.

24:45.552 --> 24:46.786
OKAY.

24:52.258 --> 24:53.593
GOT TO LOVE CELLPHONES.

24:53.593 --> 24:55.361
IT'S LIKE A LOJACK
EVEN WHEN YOU TURN IT OFF.

24:55.361 --> 24:56.563
WE GOT A 20
ON THE HUSBAND?

24:56.563 --> 24:57.897
YEAH. WE WILL.

24:57.897 --> 25:01.634
JUDGE APPROVED IT,
SENDING IT TO VERIZON NOW.

25:01.634 --> 25:05.037
WHO DO YOU THINK
STARTED THE AFFAIR?

25:05.037 --> 25:06.338
DOES IT MATTER?

25:06.338 --> 25:08.040
I HAD THIS BABYSITTER.

25:08.040 --> 25:11.077
IT WAS A CRAZY FRIEND
OF MY WIFE'S.

25:11.077 --> 25:13.680
JUST COME BY THE HOUSE
AND...I DON'T KNOW.

25:13.680 --> 25:16.148
I USED TO GET REAL STRANGE VIBES
OFF OF HER,

25:16.148 --> 25:19.151
LIKE SHE WAS SENDING ME
A SIGNAL, YOU KNOW?

25:19.151 --> 25:20.519
SIGNAL.

25:20.519 --> 25:22.121
YEAH.

25:22.121 --> 25:25.491
YEAH, THE, YOU KNOW, "YOU CAN
HAVE IT IF YOU WANT IT" SIGNAL.

25:25.491 --> 25:28.427
OOH. YOU GET
A LOT OF SIGNALS, HUH?

25:28.427 --> 25:30.362
BEING SO IRRESISTIBLE.
[ LAUGHING ]

25:30.362 --> 25:34.567
I'M JUST SAYING, MAYBE SHE WAS
LURING HIM IN, YOU KNOW?

25:34.567 --> 25:37.069
I MEAN, SHE IS AN ILLEGAL
LIVING IN A DUMP

25:37.069 --> 25:40.539
WITH HER SISTER DOWN ON UNION,
TAKING CARE OF THE MAN'S KIDS.

25:40.539 --> 25:43.610
PERHAPS SHE THOUGHT
SHE WAS MORE OF A WIFE
TO HIM THAN HIS OWN WIFE.

25:43.610 --> 25:45.411
PERHAPS SHE WAS CRAZY.

25:45.411 --> 25:47.479
PERHAPS IT WAS A SUICIDE.

25:47.479 --> 25:50.049
SO, THEN,
WHO GOT HER PREGNANT?

25:50.049 --> 25:51.283
WHO KNOWS?

25:51.283 --> 25:53.385
POINT IS THIS. HE WAS MARRIED.
SHE KNEW HE WAS MARRIED.

25:53.385 --> 25:56.188
NO MATTER WHAT HE PROMISED HER,
HE SHOULD HAVE BEEN OFF LIMITS.

25:56.188 --> 25:58.424
OH. OKAY.
SO IT'S ALL HER FAULT.

25:58.424 --> 25:59.992
HELL, YEAH!

25:59.992 --> 26:03.329
EITHER WAY,
HE HAS TO LIVE WITH IT.

26:06.332 --> 26:07.800
ALL HER FAULT.

26:07.800 --> 26:11.203
FREAKY HO'S WORKING
IN HIS HOUSE.

26:11.203 --> 26:13.205
HE JUST SLIPPED
AND FELL IN THE PUSSY, RIGHT?

26:13.205 --> 26:14.273
[ LAUGHS ]

26:14.273 --> 26:15.808
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

26:15.808 --> 26:18.911
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

26:24.016 --> 26:25.351
Sammy:
GOOD AFTERNOON, SIR.

26:25.351 --> 26:27.854
GET OUT OF THE DAMN CAR!
GET OUT OF THE CAR!

26:27.854 --> 26:29.388
NO!
GET OUT OF HERE!

26:29.388 --> 26:31.057
[ TIRES SCREECH ]
RONNIE PUT YOU UP
TO THIS?

26:31.057 --> 26:33.025
LET ME GO!
DID RONNIE
PUT YOU UP TO THIS?

26:33.025 --> 26:34.894
I CAN'T GO TO JAIL,
OKAY?

26:34.894 --> 26:37.129
PLEASE, I'VE GOT TO DO THIS.
PLEASE!

26:37.129 --> 26:39.431
ALL RIGHT,
NOBODY'S GOING TO JAIL.

26:39.431 --> 26:42.702
DADDY WILL KILL HER.
OKAY, YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

26:42.702 --> 26:45.371
PLEASE, THAT'S WHY THEY FOUGHT,
OVER ME.

26:45.371 --> 26:47.874
I HAVE TO DO THIS.

27:01.287 --> 27:02.789
UH-OH.

27:02.789 --> 27:05.892
[ CHUCKLES ]
I KNOW THAT LOOK.

27:05.892 --> 27:09.628
SOMEBODY'S GOING INTO
THE PRINCIPAL'S OFFICE.

27:09.628 --> 27:11.097
I HOPE IT'S JUICY.

27:11.097 --> 27:14.066
DID YOU FINALLY GET CAUGHT
PLAYING GRAB-ASS WITH COOPER?

27:14.066 --> 27:15.201
HUH?

27:15.201 --> 27:18.971
SNATCH A COUPLE OF KILOS
OFF THE LAST DRUG BUST?

27:18.971 --> 27:20.606
COME ON,
YOU CAN TELL ME.

27:20.606 --> 27:22.041
IT'S UNCLE DEWEY.

27:22.041 --> 27:24.176
DID YOU LEAVE YOUR GUN
IN MICKEY D's BATHROOM?

27:24.176 --> 27:26.779
SOMEBODY USE IT
TO SHOOT UP THE MAYOR?

27:29.248 --> 27:30.850
KID I SHOT'S STABLE.

27:30.850 --> 27:33.920
THAT'S SUPPOSED TO BE
BAD NEWS?

27:36.588 --> 27:38.190
SHIT.

27:38.190 --> 27:40.760
I'VE BEEN IN FRONT OF THE BOARD
OF RIGHTS THREE TIMES, MAN,

27:40.760 --> 27:42.795
AND I'M STILL HERE.

27:42.795 --> 27:44.797
YOU WANT TO KNOW
MY SECRET?

27:44.797 --> 27:46.432
NOT REALLY.

27:46.432 --> 27:48.500
I DON'T CARE.

27:48.500 --> 27:51.170
THEY'RE GONNA SAY WHATEVER
THE HELL THEY'RE GONNA SAY.

27:51.170 --> 27:53.706
YOU CAN'T CHANGE
WHAT HAPPENED.

27:53.706 --> 27:56.608
IT'S BETWEEN YOU AND GOD.

27:56.608 --> 28:02.882
IF YOU CAN LIVE WITH IT...
NOBODY CAN STOP YOU.

28:05.284 --> 28:07.419
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:09.221 --> 28:11.290
[ SIGHS ]

28:16.963 --> 28:18.530
[ DOOR OPENS ]
Hill: TANG?

28:18.530 --> 28:20.933
YES, SIR?
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?
YEAH.

28:20.933 --> 28:22.468
THE CAPTAIN
ON YOUR ORAL BOARDS

28:22.468 --> 28:24.136
HAS TO FLY TO NEW YORK
ON A PERSONAL MATTER TOMORROW,

28:24.136 --> 28:25.872
SO HE WANTS TO PUSH UP
YOUR INTERVIEW A DAY,

28:25.872 --> 28:27.539
GET IT DONE
BEFORE HE GOES.

28:27.539 --> 28:29.976
TODAY.
YEAH, IF YOU'RE READY.

28:29.976 --> 28:31.177
YES, SIR. ABSOLUTELY.

28:31.177 --> 28:32.945
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL TELL HIM.

28:38.250 --> 28:40.052
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING, MAN?

28:40.052 --> 28:41.788
WE STILL GOT AN HOUR LEFT
ON THE SHIFT.

28:41.788 --> 28:43.689
I TOLD RUCKER
I WAS FEELING HYPER-VIGILANT

28:43.689 --> 28:45.257
AND NEEDED SOME DOWN TIME.

28:47.093 --> 28:49.728
MOM'S NOT TALKING.
NO SURPRISE THERE.

28:49.728 --> 28:52.264
DCFS JUST SHOWED UP.

28:52.264 --> 28:54.867
YEAH, DEEDEE WHAT'S-HER-NAME
AGAIN?

28:54.867 --> 28:57.103
NO, IT'S THE ONE
YOU YELLED AT -- OLIVER.

28:57.103 --> 28:59.471
BUT SHE PROMISED
TO PUT THE KID IN FOSTER CARE.

28:59.471 --> 29:01.640
SHOULD HAVE DONE IT
THE FIRST TIME.

29:01.640 --> 29:03.409
[ LOCKER DOOR SLAMS ]

29:03.409 --> 29:07.313
I KNOW THAT LOOK.
JUST GOT TO LET IT GO.

29:07.313 --> 29:11.650
HEAD HOME, SHOOT HOOPS,
GO TO THE GYM,

29:11.650 --> 29:15.687
DO WHATEVER IT IS YOU GOT TO DO,
BUT JUST GO HOME, MAN.

29:15.687 --> 29:17.123
I'M FINE.

29:17.123 --> 29:19.725
THERE'S A MAGIC CHAIR AT HOME
WITH MY NAME ON IT.

29:19.725 --> 29:21.760
DOESN'T EVEN NEED QUARTERS.

29:21.760 --> 29:23.629
JUST A TV REMOTE.

29:23.629 --> 29:27.266
MIGHT EVEN READ A BOOK.

29:29.568 --> 29:31.804
Tang: I'VE WORKED WITH
A NUMBER OF EXCELLENT SERGEANTS

29:31.804 --> 29:33.472
DURING MY TIME ON THE JOB,

29:33.472 --> 29:35.875
AND I FEEL I'VE LEARNED
VALUABLE LEADERSHIP LESSONS

29:35.875 --> 29:37.276
FROM ALL OF THEM, SIR.

29:37.276 --> 29:39.345
Deputy Chief: AS A SERGEANT,
WHAT CHARACTERISTICS

29:39.345 --> 29:42.514
DO YOU BELIEVE ARE ESSENTIAL
FOR EFFECTIVE LEADERSHIP?

29:42.514 --> 29:45.918
EFFECTIVE LEADERSHIP IS ABOUT
MAKING QUICK, INFORMED DECISIONS

29:45.918 --> 29:47.286
AND STANDING BY THEM.

29:47.286 --> 29:49.088
I FEEL I CAN BRING
THIS TYPE OF LEADERSHIP

29:49.088 --> 29:51.157
TO ANY COMMAND
WHERE I AM ASSIGNED.

29:52.558 --> 29:54.994
I'M SURE YOU'VE ALL BEEN BRIEFED
ON THE RECENT SHOOTING

29:54.994 --> 29:57.663
I WAS INVOLVED IN,
AND IT MAY HAVE GIVEN YOU PAUSE.

29:57.663 --> 30:00.266
RATHER THAN DISQUALIFYING ME
FROM PROMOTION,

30:00.266 --> 30:03.002
I THINK IT SHOWS WHY
I'M AN EXCELLENT CANDIDATE.

30:03.002 --> 30:04.670
I WAS IN A HOT-FOOT PURSUIT.

30:04.670 --> 30:06.172
THE SUSPECT TURNED,

30:06.172 --> 30:08.640
AND THE REPLICA GUN
HE POINTED AT ME LOOKED REAL.

30:08.640 --> 30:11.978
I FEEL TERRIBLE
ABOUT THIS TEENAGER BEING SHOT.

30:11.978 --> 30:14.847
BUT IF I WAS IN THE ACADEMY
IN THE SIMULATOR,

30:14.847 --> 30:18.250
I WOULD HAVE DONE THE SAME EXACT
THING IN THE SAME EXACT WAY.

30:18.250 --> 30:19.886
I CAN LIVE WITH THE CONSEQUENCES

30:19.886 --> 30:22.855
AS LONG AS I KNOW THAT I WAS
PRESERVING THE SAFETY OF THOSE

30:22.855 --> 30:24.991
WHO I'M SWORN TO PROTECT.

30:24.991 --> 30:26.492
THAT'S THE JOB.

30:26.492 --> 30:27.659
YOU CAN'T DO IT RIGHT

30:27.659 --> 30:30.329
UNLESS YOU'RE PREPARED
TO MAKE THOSE DECISIONS.

30:47.379 --> 30:48.948
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

30:48.948 --> 30:50.516
ERIC HANSON?

30:50.516 --> 30:53.819
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

30:53.819 --> 30:56.522
DETECTIVE ADAMS
AND ROBINSON.

30:56.522 --> 30:57.924
ARE YOU ERIC HANSON?

30:57.924 --> 30:59.325
Eric: YES.

30:59.325 --> 31:01.493
WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO
GET IN CONTACT WITH YOU ALL DAY.

31:01.493 --> 31:03.029
YOU CHECK YOUR MESSAGES?

31:03.029 --> 31:06.765
OH, NO.
ARE MY WIFE AND KIDS OKAY?

31:06.765 --> 31:08.200
THEY'RE FINE.

31:08.200 --> 31:11.470
BUT YOUR NANNY,
VERONICA JUAREZ, IS DEAD.

31:11.470 --> 31:13.039
OH, MY GOD.

31:13.039 --> 31:15.807
AND SHE WAS PREGNANT.

31:15.807 --> 31:17.643
SHE -- WHAT?

31:17.643 --> 31:22.081
SHE WAS SENDING YOU
SOME VERY PROVOCATIVE
PICTURES AND TEXTS.

31:23.582 --> 31:25.451
OH, NO, MAN.
HELL, NO.

31:25.451 --> 31:28.420
NO, I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE IMPLYING.
I NEVER SLEPT WITH HER.

31:28.420 --> 31:31.557
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT ONE,
PLAYER?

31:31.557 --> 31:33.725
[ SIGHS ]
LOOK, I MADE A MISTAKE ONCE,

31:33.725 --> 31:37.029
WHEN SHE WAS STAYING AT
THE HOUSE WHEN MY WIFE WAS GONE.

31:37.029 --> 31:38.897
I LET THINGS GO
A LITTLE TOO FAR,

31:38.897 --> 31:42.268
BUT WE NEVER --
I MEAN, I NEVER...

31:42.268 --> 31:45.204
SHE STARTED SENDING PICTURES,
CALLING ME ALL THE TIME.

31:45.204 --> 31:47.873
SO WHY DIDN'T YOU
FIRE HER?

31:47.873 --> 31:51.944
[ SIGHS ]
CHERYL -- SHE LOVED HER.

31:51.944 --> 31:53.312
THE KIDS.

31:53.312 --> 31:56.382
FIRING HER WOULD HAVE
MADE CHERYL ASK WHY.

31:56.382 --> 32:00.119
I THOUGHT WE COULD
PHASE HER OUT.

32:00.119 --> 32:04.490
LISTEN, YOU CAN DNA ME
IF YOU WANT. IT'S THE TRUTH.
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

32:04.490 --> 32:07.459
I CAN BE TEMPTED LIKE ANY MAN,
BUT I LOVE MY WIFE.

32:07.459 --> 32:10.429
I KEPT -- I KEPT IT
IN MY PANTS, YOU KNOW?
ADAMS.

32:10.429 --> 32:12.464
WHAT?

32:14.666 --> 32:15.934
HAS MY WIFE SEEN THESE?

32:15.934 --> 32:17.003
YEP.

32:17.003 --> 32:19.671
OKAY. ALL RIGHT, THANKS.

32:24.476 --> 32:27.513
THE SECURITY GUARD FROM THE
PARKING GARAGE THIS MORNING --

32:27.513 --> 32:30.249
HE JUST TASERED A GUY
WHO TRIED TO ASSAULT A WOMAN

32:30.249 --> 32:32.384
GETTING OUT OF HER CAR.

32:32.384 --> 32:33.419
UNH.

32:33.419 --> 32:35.654
THEY JUST BROUGHT HIM
TO THE STATION.

32:35.654 --> 32:39.025
UH, THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME,
MR. HANSON.

32:41.160 --> 32:43.729
YOU MIGHT WANT TO
GET A ROOM FOR TONIGHT.

32:43.729 --> 32:44.997
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

32:44.997 --> 32:47.333
JUST WARNING YOU,
BROTHER.

32:57.709 --> 32:59.178
[ SIGHS ]

33:02.848 --> 33:06.018
[ TURN SIGNAL CLICKING ]

33:24.070 --> 33:26.605
[ RAP MUSIC PLAYING ]

34:05.043 --> 34:07.513
[ GRUNTS ]

34:09.181 --> 34:12.551
[ GRUNTING ]

34:23.929 --> 34:25.731
GET UP.

34:25.731 --> 34:26.798
GET IN THE CAR.

34:26.798 --> 34:28.667
[ GRUNTS ]

34:28.667 --> 34:31.370
GET IN THE CAR.

34:34.106 --> 34:36.208
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

34:36.208 --> 34:39.077
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

34:45.617 --> 34:47.819
[ GRUNTS ]

34:49.921 --> 34:52.624
[ GRUNTING ]

34:57.129 --> 34:58.230
AAAH!

34:58.230 --> 35:00.366
AAAAAH!

35:00.366 --> 35:03.269
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

35:17.483 --> 35:20.519
Ruben: HE WENT BACK TO
THE SAME GARAGE IN THE SAME DAY?

35:20.519 --> 35:22.721
THANK GOODNESS
FOR STUPID CRIMINALS, HUH?

35:22.721 --> 35:24.490
HE WAS SO TWEAKED

35:24.490 --> 35:26.725
THAT HE TOLD THE UNIFORMS
WHAT HAPPENED AS SOON
AS THEY HOOKED HIM UP.

35:26.725 --> 35:28.327
THEY MIRANDIZE HIM?

35:28.327 --> 35:30.061
HE WAIVED HIS RIGHTS.

35:30.061 --> 35:32.030
HE SAID HE WENT TO GRAB
THE HISPANIC LADY'S PURSE.

35:32.030 --> 35:35.734
SHE GOT SCARED, BACKED UP,
AND FLIPPED OVER THE RAILING.

35:35.734 --> 35:37.536
HE STILL COULD HAVE
PUSHED HER.

35:37.536 --> 35:39.838
WELL, THE WOMAN DIED DURING
THE COMMISSION OF A FELONY,

35:39.838 --> 35:43.442
SO IT'S STILL MURDER TWO NO
MATTER HOW THE D.A. SLICES IT.

35:43.442 --> 35:44.343
MAN.

35:44.343 --> 35:45.844
WHAT ABOUT MR. HANSON?

35:45.844 --> 35:48.747
SHOWED HIS WIFE THOSE PICTURES.
HE AIN'T EVEN DO ANYTHING.

35:48.747 --> 35:50.749
HE DIDN'T, HUH?

35:50.749 --> 35:52.651
OH, YOU STILL THINK
HE KNOCKED HER UP.

35:52.651 --> 35:55.387
WHO KNOWS?
IT'S HIS MESS NOW.

35:57.155 --> 35:59.258
COLD BLOODED.

35:59.258 --> 36:03.094
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYING ]

36:03.094 --> 36:05.697
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

36:08.200 --> 36:09.368
[ SIGHS ]

36:09.368 --> 36:12.504
INTERESTING PLACE
FOR A MEET.

36:12.504 --> 36:14.706
TESTING YOUR WILLPOWER?

36:14.706 --> 36:18.477
OXY HAS ALWAYS BEEN
MY DRUG OF CHOICE.

36:18.477 --> 36:21.980
WELL, HOW 'BOUT A LITTLE
COMPASSION FOR YOUR SPONSOR?

36:21.980 --> 36:23.582
[ SNIFFS ]

36:23.582 --> 36:27.819
I ALREADY ORDERED YOU
AN OVERPRICED FANCY WATER.

36:27.819 --> 36:29.855
[ SNIFFS ]

36:32.791 --> 36:35.661
I USED TO BUST DEALERS IN HERE
WHEN I WAS WORKING NARCO.

36:35.661 --> 36:36.995
[ SIGHS ]

36:36.995 --> 36:39.931
COME DOWN HERE TO SCORE?

36:39.931 --> 36:41.333
THINKING ABOUT IT.

36:41.333 --> 36:44.303
STILL THINKING ABOUT IT?

36:44.303 --> 36:47.939
EVERY MINUTE
OF EVERY DAY.

36:47.939 --> 36:50.642
YOU EVER GET OVER THAT?

36:50.642 --> 36:51.577
NOPE.

36:52.844 --> 36:57.048
BUT IT GETS EASIER,
SLOWLY.

36:57.048 --> 36:58.484
[ SIGHS ]

36:58.484 --> 37:00.419
SO,
WHY BACK HERE TONIGHT?

37:00.419 --> 37:02.821
TANG'S KID WOKE UP.

37:02.821 --> 37:04.690
MM. HE TALKING?

37:04.690 --> 37:05.724
DON'T KNOW.

37:05.724 --> 37:08.260
WELL, YOU TOLD F.I.D. THE TRUTH,
RIGHT?

37:08.260 --> 37:10.496
TOLD THEM WHAT I SAW.

37:10.496 --> 37:13.632
NOT WHAT I THOUGHT
HAPPENED.

37:13.632 --> 37:15.000
WHAT MIGHT HAVE HAPPENED.

37:15.000 --> 37:19.104
YOU WEREN'T THERE,
AND YOU'RE NOT CLAIRVOYANT.

37:19.104 --> 37:20.606
RIGHT.

37:20.606 --> 37:24.510
THEY CALL YOU BACK IN, ANSWER
THEIR QUESTIONS TRUTHFULLY.

37:24.510 --> 37:26.044
NO MORE, NO LESS.

37:26.044 --> 37:28.614
THAT SIMPLE.

37:28.614 --> 37:29.981
YEAH.

37:29.981 --> 37:32.584
ALL THE HARD THINGS ARE.

37:35.854 --> 37:36.988
COME ON.

37:36.988 --> 37:40.726
I KNOW A CHEAP MEXICAN JOINT
ON LINCOLN.

37:42.361 --> 37:44.296
I'M BUYING.

37:48.266 --> 37:50.669
HEY.

37:50.669 --> 37:52.771
GOD GRANT US THE SERENITY

37:52.771 --> 37:56.141
TO ACCEPT THE THINGS
WE CAN'T CHANGE.

37:56.141 --> 37:57.509
RIGHT?

38:02.748 --> 38:03.982
[ SIZZLING ]

38:03.982 --> 38:06.084
MMM.
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

38:06.084 --> 38:07.886
SMELLS GOOD.

38:07.886 --> 38:09.555
[ KEYS CLATTER ]

38:09.555 --> 38:11.823
I'M GONNA TAKE A SHOWER
BEFORE DINNER.

38:11.823 --> 38:14.693
YOUR CHILD NEEDS TO KNOW
WHERE HE COMES FROM.

38:14.693 --> 38:16.595
HE NEEDS TO KNOW
HIS STORY.

38:16.595 --> 38:19.765
HE'S GONNA HATE YOU IF YOU
DON'T TELL HIM THE TRUTH.

38:19.765 --> 38:23.569
AND TERRELL --
HE'S GONNA HATE YOU, TOO.

38:23.569 --> 38:27.339
DO THINK IT'S FAIR
TO DO THIS TO HIM?

38:27.339 --> 38:30.175
I'M NOT DOING ANYTHING
TO TERRELL.

38:30.175 --> 38:33.244
HE'S MARRIED, HAS BABIES.

38:33.244 --> 38:35.647
YOU WERE RAISED BETTER.

38:37.849 --> 38:41.720
HE DOESN'T EVEN KNOW
YOU'RE PREGNANT, DOES HE?

38:41.720 --> 38:46.024
NOT GONNA BUST UP
HIS FAMILY.

38:46.024 --> 38:47.158
OH.

38:47.158 --> 38:50.762
SO THAT'S HOW YOU PLAN
TO PUT A NOBLE FACE ON IT.

38:50.762 --> 38:53.899
YOU DIDN'T MARRY HIM WHEN HE WAS
FREE AND CLEAR AND WANTED TO,

38:53.899 --> 38:56.935
AND THEN YOU GO BACK AROUND
AND GET WHAT YOU WANT,

38:56.935 --> 38:58.604
EVEN THOUGH
YOU KNOW BETTER.

38:58.604 --> 39:00.071
MOM,
IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE.

39:00.071 --> 39:01.607
YES, IT IS THAT SIMPLE.

39:01.607 --> 39:04.610
IT'S ALL ABOUT YOU,
NOT HIM.

39:04.610 --> 39:07.846
IT'S ALWAYS BEEN
ALL ABOUT YOU.

39:07.846 --> 39:10.215
[ SIGHS ]
GOT TO GO TO THE BATHROOM.

39:10.215 --> 39:11.817
WATCH THE CHICKEN,
PLEASE.

39:16.488 --> 39:18.757
[ CLANK ]

39:22.293 --> 39:24.295
[ SCOFFS ]
[ GLASS CLINKS ]

39:24.295 --> 39:27.165
[ SIGHS ]

39:27.165 --> 39:29.968
[ TAPS FOOT ]

39:29.968 --> 39:34.606
[ RUSTLING ]

39:37.843 --> 39:39.845
LEFT MY CAR.

39:39.845 --> 39:40.946
WHAT?

39:43.815 --> 39:45.951
MY CAR --
I LEFT IT THERE.

39:45.951 --> 39:48.053
JUST PICK IT UP
TOMORROW.

39:53.592 --> 39:55.093
[ SCOFFS ]

39:55.093 --> 39:57.596
HE'S NOT GONNA REPORT IT.

39:58.930 --> 40:02.167
HOW'S HE GONNA MANHANDLE HIS
GIRLS IF HE JUST GOT MANHANDLED?

40:15.213 --> 40:17.148
YOU'RE MY PARTNER.

40:17.148 --> 40:18.750
I'LL BACK YOU UP

40:18.750 --> 40:21.453
PUNCH FOR PUNCH,
BULLET FOR BULLET.

40:21.453 --> 40:24.255
BUT I'M NOT
GIVING YOU MY HOUSE.

40:24.255 --> 40:26.725
I'M NOT
GIVING YOU MY PENSION.

40:26.725 --> 40:29.695
AND I'M NOT GONNA
GIVE YOU MY FREEDOM.

40:32.931 --> 40:35.901
DON'T EVER
DO ANYTHING LIKE THAT AGAIN.

40:45.110 --> 40:46.845
[ DOOR OPENS ]
